item.title: The 15 Steps of Selling Your Home
item.description:
The 15 Steps of Selling Your Home

By Elizabeth Weintraub Updated December 16, 2014. Whether you are selling for sale by owner as a FSBO or hiring a listing agent, the home selling process is identical. It may vary slightly from state to state, but since California tends to set the standard for much of the country, this format will address how homes are sold in California.
